  "title": "Senior Sales Manager (Consumer, Retail, Logistics)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Sales Manager (Consumer, Retail, Logistics)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As a <strong>Senior Sales Manager (Consumer, Retail, Logistics), </strong>you will be<strong> </strong>responsible for managing IT Services and IT Solutions in the Consumer, Retail, and Logistics sector.  You will be part of an Account team responsible for managing the relationship with the customer and driving profitability and growth.<br>\n <br>\n <u><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive Sales revenue and growth in the Consumer, Retail and Logistics sector.</li>\n  <li>Involved in handling Consultative selling of IT Outsourcing Services and IT      Solutions.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for preparation of Proposal and SOWs.</li>\n  <li>Good in managing different Stakeholders and VIPs such as Procurement, Legal      team.</li>\n  <li>Good in Contract negotiations and Lead negotiations for proposals.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Proven track record in Sales Management with good revenue growth on IT Outsourcing      Services and IT Solutions.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong in handling <strong>IT Outsourcing services and IT Solutions in the Consumer, Retail, and Logistics sector (CRL).</strong></li>\n  <li>Consultative selling of outsourcing services and IT Solutions</li>\n  <li>Minimum 8 experience in the IT Consulting and IT Services market.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 6 years of experience in Account Management / Business Development in the      Consulting &amp; IT Services market.</li>\n  <li>Tertiary Qualification in IT/Computer Scient/related discipline</li>\n  <li>Prior experience of managing clients in the Retail and CPG vertical.</li>\n  <li>Ability to do consultative selling of outsourcing services and IT Solutions.</li>\n  <li>Incumbent must be willing to Travel as per business needs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p>\n<p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p>\n<p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>\n<p><br></p>",
